    <item>
      <title>当共和党辩论削减范围时，特朗普的税收法案是中心舞台</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/trump-s-tax-bill-takes-center-stage-as-gop-debates-scope-of-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一返回华盛顿的国会共和党人将应对他们迄今为止最艰难的考验，谈判大规模的税收法案方案，以使唐纳德·特朗普总统获得签名的立法胜利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/trump-s-tax-bill-takes-center-stage-as-gop-debates-scope-of-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国确认2Q债务发行，将重新引入7年债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/germany-confirms-second-quarter-debt-issuance-of-92-5-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国金融机构确认，第二季度将出售925亿欧元（1000亿美元）的联邦政府债务，并宣布计划在下半年重新引入7年债券的销售。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/germany-confirms-second-quarter-debt-issuance-of-92-5-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 09:00:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国PM在Thaksin的影响下，经济失败</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/thai-opposition-assails-pm-for-economic-failures-thaksin-clout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国的主要反对党指责总理佩滕塔尔·辛纳瓦特拉（Paetongtarn Shinawatra）允许她的亿万富翁父亲塔克辛·辛纳瓦特拉（Thaksin Shinawatra）不适当地影响了政府的政策，并就关键的经济问题进行了努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/thai-opposition-assails-pm-for-economic-failures-thaksin-clout</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 06:14:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
